{
  "stem": "18186.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 349.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what we did, we did-- we had to go-- there wasn't enough food so we had to go and stay in line for everything that they-- that we needed-- sugar, bread.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was always lines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Always lines.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't like going into the store and shop like it was before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always-- anything-- there was every day they had something else in the store for-- not-- I'm not talking about clothing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Food.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Food was very-- wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Scarce.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I assume this was like in Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the way it was in Russia at that time too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Russia, you always stay [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means lines for everyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think now it's different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Communists, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Communist party can, you know, they wanted us to convert to the party, you know, to believe it to be Communist and things like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because all of a sudden, like, say before we find out the war has break-- was broke out, everybody around went out to shop, shop, shop because we didn't know how long it's going to last.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, and then they came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have-- we had to stay in line for everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe it was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't really remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody, everybody.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russia?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was a change because the-- in-- before the Russian came in and the Polish occupation was, everybody got-- had a home business.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they came, of course, they made every business their own-- that it belonged to the-- to the Communists, to the Russians, I mean, to the government.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what-- that's what changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and otherwise, I don't think it changed much more than that, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
